 and over  million tourists annually midamerican energy holdings company now berkshire hathaway energy a subsidiary of berkshire hathaway acquired nv energy in a transaction completed on december    nv energy will continue to be based in las vegas under its current name prior to the acquisition by midamerican the companys common stock was listed on the new york stock exchange under the ticker symbol nve contents  history  service reliability  customer service reputation  electric sources  major projects  subsidiaries  references  external links historyedit nv energy is the product of the  merger of the two major utilities in nevada—northern nevadas sierra pacific power based in reno and las vegas nevada power sierra pacific power was founded in  from a merger of several companies dating back to the gold rush of the s in  it reorganized as a holding company sierra pacific resources nevada power was formed in  as the consolidated power and telephone company of nevada it sold off its telephone operations in  and became southern nevada power changing its name to nevada power in  a year later it became the first nevadabased company listed on the new york stock exchange in  sierra pacific and nevada power merged sierra pacific resources was the nominal survivor with nevada power joining sierra pacific power as one of its operating companies however headquarters moved from reno to nevada powers old campus in las vegas the merger created a company with a service territory stretching over  square miles—nearly all of nevadas densely populated area on september   nevada power and sierra pacific power began doing business as nv energy this is the result of the corporate decision to unify its image under a single brand later sierra pacific resources changed its corporate name to nv energy inc in  nv energy sold its california operations to a partnership of algonquin power  utilities and emera algonquin later bought out emera service reliabilityedit entrance to nv energy corporate headquarters based on the reliability of electric distribution service nv energy ranked among the best  of electric utilities nationwide in   and  and was the best in the nation in  the rankings are based on interruption frequency and interruption duration compared to a peer group constructed by the edison electric institute customer service reputationedit nv energy has recently made a number of customer service improvements including online access to account and energy use information httpsnvenergymediaroomcomindexphpsitem revamping its ivr system and providing  customer service httpsnvenergymediaroomcomindexphpsitem electric sourcesedit the company serves its customers through a variety of sources including natural gas and renewable energy the company is currently exceeding nevadas renewable portfolio standard httpsnvenergymediaroomcomindexphpsitem of  percent of its total energy sales nv energy’s northern nevada operating company achieved a  percent renewable energy and renewable energy credit level and southern nevada achieved a  percent renewable portfolio standard  see more at httpsnvenergymediaroomcomindexphpsitemsthashpdpidpuf major projectsedit in may  the company completed construction of the harry allen gasfired generating plant below budget and ahead of schedule previously announced plans to construct two  megawatt pulverized coal generation units near ely have been cancelled prior to  the companys northern and southern nevada electric grids were not connected and ran as separate systems this changed in late  when the company completed a transmission line running from the harry allen plant north to ely nevada the kilovolt one nevada transmission line online is expected to improve electric service reliability reduce costs and allow development of renewable energy sources such as wind solar and geothermal generating units in remote parts of the state nv energy buys solar power from the  mw playa solar  project at kwh in a year power purchase agreement subsidiariesedit nevada power company sierra pacific power company referencesedit  httpswwwnvenergycomcompanycaudillcfm  nv energy bondholder report march    nv energy bondholder report march   retrieved  july    nv energy bondholder report march   retrieved  july    nv energy bondholder report march   retrieved  july    annual reports on sec form k for period ending dec   nevada power company and sierra pacific power company retrieved  july    source  annual report on form k  sec form k dated december    merger announcement  journal kathryn kranhold staff reporter of the wall street  nevada power sierra pacific plan merger deal of at least  billion wall street journal issn  retrieved    nevada power and sierra pacific power renamed nv energy press release sierra pacific resources  retrieved    update algonquin emera to jointly buy some nv energy assets reuters  retrieved    algonquin and emera announce a strategic investment agreement and the transfer of california utility to algonquin retrieved    nv energy investor presentation march  company website  saifi  saidi  las vegas reviewjournal january    jennifer robison  hot topic how does online grab you puc hears all about plan for  million power line las vegas reviewjournal   bureau of land management news release october    httpsnvenergymediaroomcomindexphpsitem  forbes july   first solar signs ppa with a record low rates  external linksedit nv energy website sources of power sierra pacific power company records nc special collections university libraries university of nevada reno v t e berkshire hathaway board of directors warren buffett chairman and ceo charlie munger howard graham buffett susan decker bill gates david gottesman charlotte guyman donald keough thomas murphy ronald olson walter scott jr insurance applied underwriters berkshire hathaway assurance berkshire hathaway homestate companies kansas bankers surety company berkshire hathaway specialty insurance boatus central states indemnity gateway underwr