ancelled prior to  the companys northern and southern nevada electric grids were not connected and ran as separate systems this changed in late  when the company completed a transmission line running from the harry allen plant north to ely nevada the kilovolt one nevada transmission line online is expected to improve electric service reliability reduce costs and allow development of renewable energy sources such as wind solar and geothermal generating units in remote parts of the state nv energy buys solar power from the  mw playa solar  project at kwh in a year power purchase agreement subsidiariesedit nevada power company sierra pacific power company referencesedit  httpswwwnvenergycomcompanycaudillcfm  nv energy bondholder report march    nv energy bondholder report march   retrieved  july    nv energy bondholder report march   retrieved  july    nv energy bondholder report march   retrieved  july    annual reports on sec form k for period ending dec   nevada power company and sierra pacific power company retrieved  july    source  annual report on form k  sec form k dated december    merger announcement  journal kathryn kranhold staff reporter of the wall street  nevada power sierra pacific plan merger deal of at least  billion wall street journal issn  retrieved    nevada power and sierra pacific power renamed nv energy press release sierra pacific resources  retrieved    update algonquin emera to jointly buy some nv energy assets reuters  retrieved    algonquin and emera announce a strategic investment agreement and the transfer of california utility to algonquin retrieved    nv energy investor presentation march  company website  saifi  saidi  las vegas reviewjournal january    jennifer robison  hot topic how does online grab you puc hears all about plan for  million power line las vegas reviewjournal   bureau of land management news release october    httpsnvenergymediaroomcomindexphpsitem  forbes july   first solar signs ppa with a record low rates  externa